<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .payment-form {
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            margin: -15px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 0px;
            margin-right: 55px;
            margin-bottom: -35px;
            height: fit-content;
        }

        .Container {
            flex-direction: row;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 800px;
            height: fit-content;
            margin: 0px auto;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: flex;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .clg-logo {
            max-width: 180px;
            max-height: 100%;
            border-right: 2px solid #000;
        }

        .image {
            height: 150px;
            width: 150px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .payment-form__header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .payment-form__title {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 0px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            padding: 2px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
        }

        .payment-form__subtitle {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #020202;
            margin-top: 0px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            padding: 2px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-family: "Tiro Devanagari Hindi", serif;
        }

        .payment-form__body {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .payment-form__subject {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            text-decoration-line: underline;
            margin-top: 0%;
        }

        .payment-form__paragraph {
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 0px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin-top: 0px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .payment-form__paragraph1 {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 0px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .payment-form__paragraph2 {
            font-size: 17px;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-top: 0px;
            text-align: justify;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .payment-form__table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            margin-left: 30px;
        }

        .payment-form__table-header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .payment-form__table-header-cell {
            padding: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #080808;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .payment-form__table-body {
            border: 1px solid #0c0c0c;
        }

        .payment-form__table-row {
            height: 40px;
        }

        .payment-form__table-cell {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #050505;
            font-weight: 400;
            color: #000;
        }

        .payment-form__table-cell1 {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #050505;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .payment-form__approval {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding-top: 20px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding-right: 20px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .payment-form__approval1 {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            padding-right: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            color: #000;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-text {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-sign {
            display: block;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-sign1 {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-end;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-sign2 {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-name {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: -20px;
        }

        .payment-form__approval-position {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #000;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .ordered-list li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-left: 30px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class='Container'>
        <div class='clg-logo'>
            <img src="/CLG-LOGO.png" alt="Description of the image" class='image' />
        </div>
        <form class="payment-form">
            <div class="payment-form__header">
                <h3 class="payment-form__subtitle">राष्ट्रीय प्रौद्योगिकी संस्थान नागालैंड</h3>
                <h3 class="payment-form__title">NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF TECHNOLOGY NAGALAND</h3>
                <h3 class="payment-form__title">Chumukedima, Nagaland-797 103</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="payment-form__body">
                <h3 class="payment-form__subject">Submitted to Director</h3>
                <div class="payment-form__approval1">
                    <div>
                        <p class="payment-form__paragraph2">
                            NIT-N/ADMN/ACAD/2024/<%= orderData['month'] %>-<%= orderData['month-number'] %>/<%= orderData['year-number'] %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <p class="payment-form__paragraph2">
                            Date: <%= orderData['today'] %>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>       
                <p class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                    Sub: NIT-N – <%= orderData['payment-type'] %> of Consumable Items Purchased for laboratory– Approval requested – regarding
                </p>
                <p class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                    Ref: 1. <%= orderData['Reference'] %>
                </p>
                <p class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                    <%= orderData.name %>, <%= orderData.Designation %>, <%= orderData.branch %> department, has submitted a request for refund for the <%= orderData['payment-type'] %> of Consumable Items purchased for <%= orderData.branch %> department Laboratory on <%= orderData['Items-Purchased-date'] %> for the purpose of <%= orderData['Purpose'] %>
                <p class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                        The amount payable towards Consumable items purchased amounts to Rs.<%= orderData['Total-amount'] %>/- (Rupees <%= orderData.amounttowords %> only) as per the
                        details enclosed. Permission may kindly be granted to sanction and disburse the above said amount to the concerned
                        Faculty mentioned above                
                </p>
                <div class="payment-form__paragraph1">
                    <b>Hence it is submitted for approval,</b>
                    <ol class="ordered-list" type="a">
                        <li>
                            Whether the payable amount of Rs.<%= orderData['Total-amount'] %>/- (Rupees <%= orderData.amounttowords %> only) shall be paid to the concerned <%= orderData.name %>, <%= orderData.Designation %>.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Whether the above amount may be paid from IRG NIT Nagaland (Account No.35747839287 / NIT-N Funds (Account No.32201262075 / 10682201001)
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                    <p class="payment-form__approval-text">'a' & 'b' for kind approval please.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-form__approval-sign1">
                    <p class="payment-form__approval-name">(Pappu Kumar Sharma)</p>
                    <p class="payment-form__approval-position">Superintendent (Acad)</p>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-form__approval">   
                    <div class="payment-form__approval-sign">
                        <p class="payment-form__approval-position">Assistant Registrar</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="payment-form__approval-sign">
                        <p class="payment-form__approval-position">Registrar</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="payment-form__approval-sign2">
                    <p class="payment-form__approval-position">Director</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
